description:
open url with your preffered app
link eye is an android app to view url before open.
first of all set link eye as default browser.
then try to open a link and you see a friendly interface to edit,copy,open or share this link.
also link eye have an extra feature and this is much like to copy to pane feature.
when you share content from other apps you can see same interface too if it's full text ( like url or text message ).
